FORM write_result  USING    p_gt_full TYPE gyt_tadir.

  LOOP AT p_gt_full ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<fs_gt_full>).
    WRITE: / <fs_gt_full>-object ,<fs_gt_full>-obj_name.
  ENDLOOP.
